      • DeviceTracker

        public DeviceTracker(java.lang.String key,
                     DeviceTracker.Type type,
                     int port)
        Constructor with options for key, data type, and device id information.
        Parameters:
        key - String representing the reference id of the tracker. Can be named anything.
        type - Type representing the data type of this tracker: conditional, numeric, or message
        port - int value representing the port number of the sensor or OI device, or its device id
        See Also:
        DeviceTracker.Type
